    printed directly in the console — you don't have to open any
    files to see your results.

${BOLD}OUTPUT${NC}
    Full logs are also saved (for later reference) under:
        ./${RESULTS_DIR}/<target>_<timestamp>/
            nmap.txt | web_recon.txt | directories.txt | ssl_report.txt

