    - Script is copied to ${INSTALL_PATH}
    - A 'scan' alias (alias scan="sudo nmap_pro") is appended to
      ~/.bashrc and ~/.zshrc if not already present
    - Missing dependencies (nmap, whatweb, nikto, gobuster, sslscan)
